chntpw: chntpw (NT SAM password recovery utility)
chntpw:
chntpw: This little program provides a way to view information and change
chntpw: user passwords in a Windows NT/2000 userdatabase file. Old passwords
chntpw: need not be known since they are overwritten. In addition it also
chntpw: contains a simple registry editor (same size data writes) and an
chntpw: hex-editor which enables you to fiddle around with bits and bytes in
chntpw: the file as you wish.
chntpw: http://home.eunet.no/~pnordahl/ntpasswd/
chntpw:
chntpw: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
